2026-05-10T21:07:13.9512885Z 12    <!--
2026-05-10T21:07:13.9513270Z 13        Required for reminders to pop as full-screen notifications over the
2026-05-10T21:07:13.9513641Z 14        lock screen when the user enables "Full-Screen Notifications" in
